Welcome to HotPot â€“ a comprehensive full-stack Online Food Delivery Platform designed for a seamless experience for users, restaurants, and administrators. This project combines a React.js frontend with a C# ASP.NET Core Web API backend and uses Microsoft SQL Server as the database.

ğŸ“š Project Overview
HotPot allows users to explore nearby restaurants, browse categorized menus, manage carts, place orders, and track delivery. Restaurants can manage their menu and orders, while admins have full control over user and restaurant management.

